@startuml Update_Blog_Policy_Sequence_Diagram
title 3.20.4 Update Blog & Policy - Sequence Diagram
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
autonumber
autoactivate on

actor "Staff/Admin" as User
boundary "Blog & Policy Form" as Form
control "ManagePublicContentController" as Controller
control "PublicContentService" as Service
entity "PublicContentDAO" as DAO
database "Database" as DB
boundary "content-list.jsp" as ListView

User -> Form: Submit updated blog or policy
Form -> Controller: POST /staff/public-content
Controller -> Controller: Read update data
Controller -> Service: save(content, currentUser)
Service -> Service: Validate content and permission
Service -> DAO: update(content)
DAO -> DB: Update blog or policy
DB --> DAO: Update result
DAO --> Service: Update result
Service --> Controller: Save successful
Controller -> ListView: Redirect to content list
ListView --> User: Display updated content list

@enduml
